Utterance: Tumi kemon achho aj? Shuni, tomake shuni. Ami thik achi, dhonnobad tomake. Tumi ke?
Oar tumi kon haate likhte sukhcho? Dike? Dike haat diye tomar memory niye kichu prashna korar jonno tomake prosno korbo, thik achi?
Tumi amake bolte paro amra kon deshe achi?
Amader building er kon floor e achi?
Ami tin ta object er naam bolbo. Ami set korar por, tader naam tomar kache repeat korte chai. Apple, table, penny.
Mone rakho tader naam. Karon ami tomar kache kichu minute porer moddhe abar tader naam bolte chai.
Ami tomake kebol ki naam bolte bolchi?
Ami chai tomake ei bhashay ekta phrase repeat korte. Phrase holo "No ifs, ands, no buts."
Ei page er upore likha gulo poro. Tarpor je likha ase, seta koro.
Ei kagaj ta dharo tomar dik theke dharo. Ekbar hath diye kagaj ta muriye rakh, tarpor kagaj ta tomar kolay niye rakh.
